ch.usi.dag.disl.snippet

Class Shadow

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.usi.dag.disl.snippet.Shadow

  • public final class Shadow
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds information about a region where a snippet will be woven. The shadow contains two type of regions. A logical region, which is available directly in the shadow, is designed mainly for static analysis and represents a region of bytecode which is logically captured by a marker. In contrast, a weaving region is designed as a guidance for the weaver, and indicates where exactly should the code be woven.
